Test Plan
Project Name:
Buyer Journey Testing

Objective:
To validate the complete buyer journey on the Sauce Demo website, ensuring that a user can log in, add items to the cart, proceed to checkout, and confirm the order successfully.

Scope:
The test covers the following functionalities:

User login with valid credentials.
Adding items to the shopping cart.
Navigating to the cart and proceeding to checkout.
Filling out checkout information.
Verifying the order confirmation.

Test Environment:
Website: https://www.saucedemo.com
Browser: Google Chrome (latest version)
Automation Tool: Robot Framework with SeleniumLibrary.

Deliverables:
Test Plan Document
Test Cases with detailed steps
Execution results with logs and screenshots (if required)
